{"tid":1524180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發生咁大件事 啲ocamp撚收皮未啊！","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:51:08.000Z","uid":160137,"like":40,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"98e6d72b7bdd6e50907886da4f343a59f6e91b90","tid":1524180,"uid":160137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"今日發生左黑警打人事件<br />\n令車廂內多名市民受傷<br />\n係呢個時候<br />\n仲有班仆街好撚開心咁po ocamp嘅嘢<br />\n仲有班仆街po船p嘅嘢<br />\n我屌哂佢地老母<br />\n所以一定要將啲pk po出黎公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wGV3Sh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wGV3Sh.png&h=423bbb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbgi1DZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftbgi1DZ.png&h=02b596b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條仆街個支莊仲要拆撚左個連儂牆！<br />\n呢個只係冰山一角 大家po出大家身邊嘅ocamp撚/港豬出嚟啦！"},{"pid":"0eb62d1fa29e40d506ee6d20e92c3e9383bd3e11","tid":1524180,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=abafa30f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea42c8c670d25cdb227b7c9f77927b429f34d1e5","tid":1524180,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/xbt92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstr